snippet.title: London Fields (Amber Heard & Jim Sturgess) - Make Out Scene
snippet.description:
London Fields (Amber Heard & Jim Sturgess) - Make Out Scene

Nicola, a clairvoyant femme fatale, lives with a premonition that she will be murdered. However, she begins a love affair with three different men at the same time.

Initial release: September 20, 2018
Director: Mathew Cullen

Amber Heard (Nicola Six)
Jim Sturgess
